# AI Museum Curator â€” Greek Mythology Edition

## Overview
This Streamlit app allows users to explore Greek gods, heroes, creatures, and related works via The MET Open API. It includes curator-level insights and AI-generated content (optional with OpenAI API key).

## Features
- **Greek Deities & Works**: Search a mythological figure and view artworks, manuscripts, books, and artifacts.  
- **AI-enhanced content**: Expanded biographies, artwork overview, historical context, and iconography.  
- **Interactive Art Zone**: Ask questions about visual details or identify mythic scenes.  
- **Grid / Expander UI**: Clean card-style layout with collapsible details.

## Installation
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py


